== Arrest In Japan ==

<blockquote>
'''Article 34.''' No person shall be arrested or detained without being at once informed of the charges against him or without the immediate privilege of counsel; nor shall he be detained without adequate cause; and upon demand of any person such cause must be immediately shown in open court in his presence and the presence of his counsel.<br/>''Translation of the Constitution of Japan''
</blockquote>

* [ http://www.nichibenren.or.jp/en/legal/arrest_01.html JFBA advice ]
* [ http://www.tlug.jp/ML/0610/msg00108.html US and British embassy advice ]
